# CodeWalkers Environment Variables Template
# ==========================================
# Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to your home directory: `cp .codewalkers.env.example ~/.codewalkers.env`
# 2. Fill in the values below with your actual credentials.
# 3. Restart the session in CodeWalkers to apply changes.

# ---------------------------------------------------------
# 1. GitHub Copilot CLI Configuration
# ---------------------------------------------------------
# Required if you want to use GitHub Copilot CLI.
# You can generate a Personal Access Token (classic or fine-grained) 
# at https://github.com/settings/tokens
GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_your_github_token_here
# Alternative names recognized by Copilot:
# COPILOT_GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_your_github_token_here
# GH_TOKEN=ghp_your_github_token_here

# ---------------------------------------------------------
# 2. Gemini CLI Configuration
# ---------------------------------------------------------
# Required if you want to use Google's Gemini CLI.
# Get your API key from Google AI Studio: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=AIzaSy_your_gemini_api_key_here

# ---------------------------------------------------------
# 3. Network Proxy Configuration
# ---------------------------------------------------------
# If you are in a region that requires a proxy to access GitHub or Google APIs,
# uncomment and set your local proxy address here.
# HTTP_PROXY=http://127.0.0.1:7890
# HTTPS_PROXY=http://127.0.0.1:7890
# ALL_PROXY=socks5://127.0.0.1:7890

# ---------------------------------------------------------
# 4. System PATH Override (Optional)
# ---------------------------------------------------------
# By default, GUI apps on macOS might not inherit your shell's PATH.
# If your CLIs (gemini, copilot, node) are installed in custom locations, 
# you can override the PATH here.
# PATH=/usr/local/bin:/opt/homebrew/bin:/usr/bin:/bin:/usr/sbin:/sbin:~/.local/bin